{"tid":1034489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉淑儀：灣區製造機遇惟政府需處理遊客及醫療等矛盾","createTime":"2019-02-24T03:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T05:55:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2652b3b09022fc12f4aea996a001930521178ac","tid":1034489,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"新民黨主席葉劉淑儀在一個電台節目表示，粵港澳大灣區對香港有很大機遇，但政府需要檢視在哪些方面對本港造成矛盾並做好管理，包括遊客、醫療服務等。她說，政制及內地事務局局長聶德權有責任跟進。<br />\n葉劉淑儀表示，不應該形成排擠內地人的心態，目前每日透過單程證配額到港家庭團聚有約130多人；他們較年輕，願意從事體力勞動工作，加上有其他引入優才的渠道，為香港補充人力資源。<br />\n她說，如果沒有人才補充到港，香港人口將不斷萎縮和老化，同時內地亦不斷吸引優才，香港在大灣區的地位將會削弱，因此不應該對新移民有狹窄的看法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80-%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%87%E6%83%9F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9C%80%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E7%AD%89%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE-020718080.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%25B7%2591%25E5%2584%2580-%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2581%2587%25E6%2583%259F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2599%2582%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%259F%259B%25E7%259B%25BE-020718080.html&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xbyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=590f4aec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80-%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%87%E6%83%9F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9C%80%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E7%AD%89%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE-020718080.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c00d84618894610c8cd2c3d677c0c85e130b884","tid":1034489,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T03:18:07.000Z","msg":"就快選區議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" clas